Package: diaggnosticplots
Type: Package
Title: Make Diagnostic Plots for predictive Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("AlexandeR", "Noll", email = "alexander.noll@hotmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: AlexandeR Noll <alexander.noll@hotmail.com>
Description: This package transforms some useful diagnostic plots for
    predictive models to the ggplot2 plotting system. These include include the
    lift plot, the gain plot and calibration plots. The computation involved
    come from the wonderful caret package.
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    ggplot2
Imports:
    caret,
    ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
